Package io.honeycomb.libhoney

Class Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.honeycomb.libhoney.Options

  • public class Options
extends Object
    Holds configuration options for HoneyClient, as well as their default values.

    All configuration options are optional, and unless explicitly set, default values will be used. For details on each option see the setter methods of the Options.Builder class, as well as the HoneyClient class documentation.
